    java.io.Serializable

    public final class CalypsoPoIllegalArgumentException
extends CalypsoPoCommandException
    The exception CalypsoPoIllegalArgumentException indicates that the input user data do not allow to build a syntactically correct command (e.g. SFI too large, record number out of bounds,...).
